    "causal_summary": "Run a bespoke deep-loop that iteratively mutates cli-devin's prompt scaffolding against documented failure-mode fixtures with actual SWE-1.6 invocations, converges on winning patterns, applies them back to the skill, then closes a file-extraction gap, propagates the cross-CLI applicable findings to the sibling skill cards, and validates the held-back findings against two frontier models (deepseek-v4-pro + kimi-k2.6) before promoting them cross-CLI. The arc moves cli-devin's defaults from \"best guess from documentation\" to \"empirically validated on three measured models with cross-CLI propagation\".",
